Description

This collection consists of records related to a June 23, 1998 telephone conversation between President Clinton and Ryutaro Hashimoto, Prime Minister of Japan. Open records include emails related to scheduling of the phone call. President Clinton wanted to discuss with Prime Minister Hashimoto the Asian financial crisis. The collection also includes memorandum, forms, and administrative paperwork related to records management in the office.
